 you need to update the number of shows that have aired, please do so directly to the program show and not here. \n\nFor example, if you want to display the number of episodes for \"The Simpsons\", you would use the following code:\n\n{{Template parameter value|The Simpsons|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n\nReplace the name of the program as needed. \n\n-->\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable mw-collapsible\" style=\"width:100%;\" text-align:center;\"\n|- \"\n! Number of<br />seasons || Series || Network || First air date || Last air date || data-sort-type=\"number\" | Number of episodes<br />\n|- style=\"background:#cfecec;\"\n| {{Template parameter value|The Simpsons|Infobox television||num_seasons|}}\n| ''[[The Simpsons]]''\n| [[FOX]]\n| 1989-12-17 \n| Present\n| {{Template parameter value|The Simpsons|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|- style=\"background:#cfecec;\"\n| {{Template parameter value|Law & Order: Special Victims Unit|Infobox television||num_seasons|}}\n| ''[[Law & Order: Special Victims Unit]]''\n| [[NBC]]\n| 1999-09-20\n| Present\n| {{Template parameter value|Law & Order: Special Victims Unit|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n| 20\n| ''[[Gunsmoke#Television series (1955-1975)|Gunsmoke]]''\n| [[CBS]]\n| 1955-09-10\n| 1975-03-31\n| 635 <!-- Not linking to Gunsmoke page on purpose -->\n|-\n| {{Template parameter value|Law & Order|Infobox television||num_seasons|}}\n| ''[[Law & Order]]''\n| NBC\n| 1990-09-13\n| 2010-05-24\n| {{Template parameter value|Law & Order|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n| 19\n| ''[[Lassie (1954 TV series)|Lassie]]''\n| CBS\n| 1954-09-12\n| 1971-03-21\n| {{Template parameter value|Lassie (1954 TV series)|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}<ref name=\"LassieLength\">''Lassie'' ran for a total of 19 seasons and 591 episodes. The final two seasons aired in syndication.</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#cfecec;\"\n| {{Template parameter value|Family Guy|Infobox television||num_seasons|}}\n| ''[[Family Guy]]''\n| FOX\n