y Central]] <small>(2008\u20132013)</small>\n| 1999-03-28\n| 2013-09-03\n| {{Template parameter value|Futurama|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n|07\n| ''[[MacGyver (1985 TV series)|MacGyver]]''\n| ABC\n| 1985-09-29\n| 1992-05-21\n|{{Template parameter value|MacGyver (1985 TV series)|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n|07\n| ''[[30 Rock]]''\n| NBC\n| 2006-10-11\n| 2013-01-31\n| {{Template parameter value|30 Rock|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n|07\n| ''[[Medium (TV series)|Medium]]''\n| NBC <small>(2005\u20132009)</small><br/>CBS <small>(2009\u20132011)</small>\n| 2005-01-03\n| 2011-01-21\n| {{Template parameter value|Medium (TV series)|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n|07\n| ''[[Cagney & Lacey]]''\n| CBS\n| 1982-03-25<ref>''Cagney & Lacey'' began with a pilot movie on October 8, 1981.</ref>\n| 1988-05-16\n| {{Template parameter value|Cagney & Lacey|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n|07\n| ''[[Parks and Recreation]]''\n| NBC\n| 2009-04-09\n| 2015-02-24\n| {{Template parameter value|Parks and Recreation|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n|07\n| ''[[Scandal (TV series)|Scandal]]''\n| ABC\n| 2012-04-05\n| 2018-04-19\n| {{Template parameter value|Scandal (TV series)|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n|07\n| ''[[Emergency!]]''\n| NBC\n| 1972-01-15\n| 1977-05-28\n| {{Template parameter value|Emergency!|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n|07\n| ''[[Homicide: Life on the Street]]''\n| NBC\n| 1993-01-31\n| 1999-05-21\n| {{Template parameter value|Homicide: Life on the Street|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n|07\n| ''[[Cheyenne (TV series)|Cheyenne]]''\n| ABC\n| 1955-09-20<ref>''Cheyenne'' began as a rotating element of ''[[Warner Bros. Presents]]''.</ref>\n| 1962-12-17\n| {{Template parameter value|Cheyenne (TV series)|Infobox television||num_episodes|}}\n|-\n|07\n| ''[[Rules of Engagement (TV series)|Rules of Engagement]]''\n| CBS\n| 2007-02-05\n| 2013-05-20\n| {{Template parameter value|Rules of Engagement (TV 