ie    |first2 = Shang-Ping\n |last3 = Liu    |first3 = Zhengyu\n |last4 = Zhu    |first4 = Jiang\n |title = Overlooked possibility of a collapsed Atlantic Meridional Overturning Circulation in warming climate\n |year = 2017\n |doi = 10.1126/sciadv.1601666\n |pmid = 28070560 |pmc = 5217057 |journal = Science Advances |volume = 3   |pages = e1601666 |number =1\n|bibcode = 2017SciA....3E1666L \n}}\n* {{cite journal   |ref=harv\n |title = High-resolution carbon dioxide concentration record 650,000\u2013800,000 years before present\n |last1 = L\u00fcthi    |first1=Dieter\n |last2 = Le Floch |first2=Martine\n |last3 = Bereiter |first3=Bernhard\n |last4 = Blunier  |first4=Thomas\n |last5 = Barnola  |first5=Jean-Marc\n |last6 = Siegenthaler |first6=Urs\n |last7 = Raynaud  |first7=Dominique\n |last8 = Jouzel   |first8=Jean\n |last9 = Fischer  |first9=Hubertus\n |display-authors = 4\n |date=2008\n |last10=Kawamura |first10=Kenji\n |last11=Stocker |first11=Thomas F.\n |journal=Nature\n |volume=453 |issue=7193 |pages=379\u2013382\n |bibcode=2008Natur.453..379L |doi=10.1038/nature06949 |pmid=18480821\n |url=https://epic.awi.de/id/eprint/18281/1/Lth2008a.pdf\n}}\n* {{Cite journal  |ref=harv\n |last1 = Marshall  |first=Burke\n |last2 = Hsiang   |first2=Solomon M.\n |last3 = Edward   |first3=Miguel\n |date=2014\n |title=Climate and Conflict\n |url=https://www.nber.org/papers/w20598\n |journal=NBER\n |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118081434/https://www.nber.org/papers/w20598\n |archive-date=18 November 2018\n |doi = 10.3386/w20598|url-status=live\n}}\n*{{Cite journal  |ref=harv\n |last1 = Matthews   |first=H. Damon\n |last2=Gillett|first2=Nathan P.\n |last3=Stott|first3=Peter A. \n |last4=Zickfeld|first4=Kirsten\n |date=2009\n |title=The proportionality of global warming to cumulative carbon emissions\n |journal=Nature\n |volume=459|issue=7248|pages=829\u2013832|doi=10.1038/nature08047|pmid=19516338 |bibcode = 2009Natur.459..829M |issn=1476-4687}}\n* {{cite journal |r